io.github.thunderbots.lightning.drive

  • Packages that use io.github.thunderbots.lightning.drive

    io.github.thunderbots.lightning.drive
    Provides classes used in the Drive Systems of robots.
    io.github.thunderbots.lightning.robot
    Provides an interface with methods needed in Robot objects
  • Classes in io.github.thunderbots.lightning.drive used by io.github.thunderbots.lightning.drive 
    Class and Description
    DriveMotorSet
    A DriveMotorSet is a collection of motors used for the sole purpose of driving the robot.
    DriveSystem
    A DriveSystem represents the motors used for driving the robot, their arrangement, and in some cases, the type of wheels attached to the motor.
    MecanumDrive
    A MecanumDrive is a DriveSystem that represents a system using mecanum wheels.
